      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POPPY POPSTAR (8) is racing in great heart with back-to-back wins last month and seconds in both outings since. Kept chasing last time over a longer distance at this venue, finishing second and less than 5 metres from the winner. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon. Primary contender. MONTANA MUSCLE (5) has been competitive since winning at Echuca last month. Kept the ball rolling last time when 3 metres from the winner at Shepparton. Likely to be there at the finish. CHRISTMAS BABE NZ (4) led from one spot wider when winning here three back and has been close-up since. Speedy so can give a sight. PLAYA DEL CARMEN (3) has been racing consistently, only once missing the top three in her last  six starts highlighted by a Maryborough win. Draws to be competitive again.",
